                                                                                             NIST SP 800-53A, REV. 5                         ASSESSING SECURITY AND PRIVACY CONTROLS IN INFORMATION SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS




                                                                                              SA-17(01)       DEVELOPER SECURITY AND PRIVACY ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN | FORMAL POLICY
                                                                                                              MODEL
                                                                                                              SA-17(01)(a)[01]      as an integral part of the development process, the developer of the system,
                                                                                                                                    system component, or system service is required to produce a formal policy model
                                                                                                                                    describing the <SA-17(01)_ODP[01] organizaonal security policy> to be enforced;

                                                                                                              SA-17(01)(a)[02]      as an integral part of the development process, the developer of the system,
                                                                                                                                    system component, or system service is required to produce a formal policy model
                                                                                                                                    describing the <SA-17(01)_ODP[02] organizaonal privacy policy> to be enforced;

                                                                                                              SA-17(01)(b)[01]      the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                    prove that the formal policy model is internally consistent and suﬃcient to enforce
                                                                                                                                    the deﬁned elements of the organizaonal security policy when implemented;
